{"tid":1259574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日626民陣集會，追究黑驚同釋放示威根本就唔係重點","createTime":"2019-06-26T15:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T15:32:43.000Z","uid":141026,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"502230c71209c800343e8f997910157b64245fa9","tid":1259574,"uid":141026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"626民陣集會重點係G20<br />\n乜你地覺得其他國家嘅元首會幫你哋做啲咁雞毛鴨蒜嘅小事<br />\n梗係聚焦香港民主化嘅情況啦<br />\n你唔會預期侵侵同習近平一齊傾呢啲<br />\n<br />\n仲有連登仔係咪失左憶<br />\n屌人哋話我要真普選令到場集會失去焦點<br />\n我屌你啊<br />\n報紙頭版上面第五個訴求唔係話爭取民主化咩<br />\n你哋自己加落去你自己都唔清楚？<br />\n人哋咁做都係和應你個國際報紙廣告<br />\n<br />\nG20 is our target <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAdd oil<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a649390475f799de374ee610612fdd9a3582ea2","tid":1259574,"uid":141026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec49fc53b8d084bdb0b6ce0638a604e049bc3fb2","tid":1259574,"uid":141026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa